<section class="how-section" id="how">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="section-label">How It Works</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Simple as <em>1, 2, 3.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub centered">No complicated routines. No pill schedules. Just two gummies and you're done.</p>

    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Take 2 Gummies</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Enjoy two wild berry flavoured gummies about 30 minutes before you want to fall asleep.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Wind Down</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">The three-ingredient formula gets to work — quieting your mind, relaxing your body, signalling it's time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Wake Up Refreshed</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">No groggy alarm. No 3am wake-up. Just you, rested and ready. This is what sleep is supposed to feel like.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

